import express from "express"
import routes from "../routes";

import {home, login, photos, profile} from "../controllers/globalController"


const globalRouter = express.Router();

globalRouter.get(routes.home, home) 
globalRouter.get(routes.login, login) 
globalRouter.get(routes.photos, photos) 
globalRouter.get(routes.profile, profile) 

export default globalRouter

import express from "express"
import routes from "../routes"
import { documentation, buy, refund, remove, edit } from "../controllers/commonController";

const apiRouter = express.Router(); 

apiRouter.get(routes.documentation, documentation)
apiRouter.get(routes.buy, buy)
apiRouter.get(routes.refund,refund)
apiRouter.get(routes.remove, remove)
apiRouter.get(routes.edit, edit)

export default apiRouter
